AVOID THIS RESTAURANT: MISTREATMENT OF THE ELDERLY AND INCOMPETENT BEHAVIOR.  The service was incompetent and engaged in discrimination against the elderly. Yesterday, I ordered spaghetti with meatsauce on behalf of my household where my 95 year old grandfather and my near-70 year old aunt reside.  I was working and unavailable so I expected, as usual, that the delivery would come to my elderly relatives at their door.  When the driver called me saying she had arrived, I told her to come upstairs to the apartment by taking the elevators.  I also reminded her that the building in which I live, the desk/concierge always allows people up to make a quick delivery.  She then said someone (who I later learned was a new college student) stopped her and I told her to ignore whatever he said (as the desk/concierge was not following normal protocol at that moment) and come upstairs; the delivery lady then said it would be no problem.  I noticed I had not heard back after sometime and then called her back and then learned that she refused to come up.  I gave her the instructions on how to come up and she did not want to comply.  I then called her manager and he was absolutely incompetent and childish when I spoke to him on the phone.  He kept claiming that the desk would not let his driver upstairs and I told him that the individual at the desk in my building is not following what the desk/concierge usually do/allow and that it was perfectly fine for the driver to come up.  I also mentioned that I spoke with my many individuals who work in the building about this issue many times since we have elderly individuals living with me and that it was okay for her to come upstairs.   He kept asking me what I wanted the driver to do, to which I replied that she should simply walk to elevators and go upstairs to the apartment.  I then found out that my aunt, who has some disabilities, had to go downstairs and the driver refused to hand the food to her.  The driver then left the building, as my aunt told me, and she never received any food.  Absolutely a case of incompetence and poor treatment of a household with elderly people.  The manager should be fired.  DO NOT PATRONIZE THIS PLACE!
